      "id": "PopularPost47379",
      "post_content": "This is a classic card for multi-color decks. It was generally a lot more useful before there was an abundance of other lands that could produce any color. Now with cards like Undiscovered Paradise, Rupture Spire, Shimmering Grotto, the \"Vivid\" lands, etc., I believe there are better options. I do like Rupture Spire because you pay the cost once and have no drawback afterwards.",
      "posted_by": "kowrip",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost47379\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">This is a classic card for multi-color decks.  It was generally a lot more useful before there was an abundance of other lands that could produce any color.  Now with cards like Undiscovered Paradise, Rupture Spire, Shimmering Grotto, the \"Vivid\" lands, etc., I believe there are better options.  I do like Rupture Spire because you pay the cost once and have no drawback afterwards.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '47379'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy16700\">kowrip</span>\r\n                                (1/22/2010 10:15:43 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmal