      "id": "PopularPost369442",
      "post_content": "The reason that this is better than Rupture Spire is that if you are playing 5 colors, than in the extra turn that you waste from Spire, you could have played the mana that you needed. Also, about life, the only life point that counts is the last one. A victory at 1 life just as great as at 10 life.",
